snippet.title: Out of Bounds by Tobías Rusjan: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
"Create" a game while "fixing" bugs in Out of Bounds! A puzzle shooter developed by Tobías Rusjan and published by Saibot Studios. Coming to Steam very soon. WISHLIST NOW!
http://oobgame.com/

Music "Head Run" by Kraftamt:
http://dig.ccmixter.org/people/Karstenholymoly

Developer's Twitter:
